  "starterCode": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<style>\ndiv {\n  background-color: lightgray;\n  /* width */\n  /* padding (inside) */\n  /* border */\n  /* margin (outside) */\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p>The CSS box model wraps every element: margin, border, padding, content.</p>\n<div>This box has all four parts of the box model.</div>\n</body>\n</html>",
  "solutionCode": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<style>\ndiv {\n  background-color: lightgray;\n  width: 300px;\n  padding: 25px;\n  border: 5px solid navy;\n  margin: 20px;\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p>The CSS box model wraps every element: margin, border, padding, content.</p>\n<div>This box has all four parts of the box model.</div>\n</body>\n</html>",
  "checks": [
